<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٤٣٥ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا عَلِيٌّ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا مَرْوَانُ: أَخْبَرَنَا هَاشِمٌ: أَخْبَرَنَا عَامِرُ بْنُ سَعْدٍ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١٧٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنْ أَبِيهِ <span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(مَنِ اصْطَبَحَ كُلَّ يَوْمٍ تَمَرَاتٍ عَجْوَةً، لَمْ يَضُرَّهُ سُمٌّ وَلَا سِحْرٌ ذَلِكَ الْيَوْمَ إِلَى اللَّيْلِ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(سَبْعَ تَمَرَاتٍ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>